pr_body:
This PR is aimed at reducing the amount of updates required.

* py3status modules now only trigger an update if their content has actually changed.

* containers (currently only groups) can now register a function that allows py3status to be aware of the active content so updates are only triggered for content that is being displayed.  If they have not registered a function then all sub-module updates trigger an update.

This leads to a reduction in overall workload.

__example:__
```
group {
    time {}
    volume_status {}
}
```

When the group shows `time` we are updated every second. When we show `volume_status` we only update when the volume has changed etc.

Implement [SemVer 2 ](http://semver.org/)

This will be used for runtime version comparison

@sjagoe

Opening this up as a PR. There's no tests yet, so we'll have to figure those out later.

@yungchin can you take a look at this? In particular, the changes in `base.py`, `partitioners.py` and `common.py` since those might affect you.  There aren't a lot of changes in there, but some worth noting.

Also, the implementation will give you a good idea of how I was thinking to do partitioners in Python.

## Summary

Excludes contenttypes app from the fixtures. I had to manually delete them, but it was an easy fix in this case. In the future use the `--exclude=contenttypes` option for `dumpdata` @66eli77.

@jamalex if you rebase after this is merged, you should be able to run tests.

First thing needed for #183.

This introduces a `diamond.collectors` `entry_point`.

What this means is a package can have:

```python
setup(
  entry_points={
    'diamond.collectors': [
      'thing = thing',
    ],
  }
)
```

and when installed, Diamond will discover and import it like any of the other included collector modules.

签名的生成与微信的[调试工具](http://mp.weixin.qq.com/debug/cgi-bin/sandbox?t=cardsign])相同，但是我在前端使用 JSSDK 调用这些参数会报错，没有找到原因。
```javascript
wx.chooseCard({
    shopId: '', // 门店Id
    cardType: '', // 卡券类型
    cardId: '', // 卡券Id
    timestamp: 0, // 卡券签名时间戳
    nonceStr: '', // 卡券签名随机串
    signType: '', // 签名方式，默认'SHA1'
    cardSign: '', // 卡券签名
    success: function (res) {
        var cardList= res.cardList; // 用户选中的卡券列表信息
    }
});
```
并且，我认为 get_jsapi_signature 也应该返回一个带有所有参数的字典，而不是只返回一个签名

- new hierarchy levels for module directories and parametrized tests;
- ability to configure report hierarchy via pytest.ini;
- generating hierarchy item name depends on configuration;
- hierarchy item result now depends on nested tests results.
